\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"경비실\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"있음\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"옥상\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"있음\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ndic</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{'층수': 8, '경비실': '있음', '옥상': '있음'}</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>values<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">dict_values([8, '있음', '있음'])</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># values</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>values<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">8\n있음\n있음</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># values</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>values<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[8, '있음', '있음']</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token builtin\">list</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>values<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[8, '있음', '있음']</code></pre></div>\n<h4>key, value 쌍 items()</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">dic <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">\"층수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"경비실\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"있음\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"옥상\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"있음\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ndic</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{'층수': 8, '경비실': '있음', '옥상': '있음'}</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>items<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">dict_items([('층수', 8), ('경비실', '있음'), ('옥상', '있음')])</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>b <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> dic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>items<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f\"key:</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> / value:</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">key:층수 / value:8\nkey:경비실 / value:있음\nkey:옥상 / value:있음</code></pre></div>","categories":["ALL","Python"],"date":"October 05, 2023","description":"파이썬 기초","id":"68261fc4-ba25-5874-9a98-bf2daf795829","keywords":["Python","기초","튜플","딕셔너리"],"slug":"/my-first-article/python/python4/","title":"[파이썬 기초] 튜플과 딕셔너리","readingTime":{"text":"7 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}